Module org.monarchinitiative.phenol.annotations
Package org.monarchinitiative.phenol.annotations.formats.hpo

Class HpoAssociationDataBuilder

java.lang.Object
org.monarchinitiative.phenol.annotations.formats.hpo.HpoAssociationDataBuilder
public class HpoAssociationDataBuilder extends Object
A builder for HpoAssociationData.

In principle, HpoAssociationData is assembled by providing the following three primary components:

  • geneIdentifiers(GeneIdentifiers),
  • diseaseToGeneAssociations(DiseaseToGeneAssociations), and
  • hpoGeneAnnotations(HpoGeneAnnotations).
However, the builder can create each component if paths or corresponding secondary components are provided.

Gene identifiers: either homoSapiensGeneInfo(Path, Set) or hgncCompleteSetArchive(Path).

Disease to gene associations: mim2GeneMedgen(Path) and orphaToGenePath(Path) (optional).

HPO gene annotations: hpoDiseases(AnnotatedItemContainer).

The builder throws MissingFormatArgumentException if any of the primary components is missing and the secondary components are not provided.
